functionDecorators.name: addModule
functionDecorators.description: Adds a module to a wallet. Cannot execute when wallet is locked (or under recovery).

functionDecorators.name: init
functionDecorators.description: Inits a Module for a wallet by e.g. setting some wallet specific parameters in storage.

functionDecorators.name: supportsStaticCall
functionDecorators.description: Returns whether the module implements a callback for a given static call method.
